body_html:
The error lines you copied are simply reports by bazel on roughly where the compilation failure happened.
Here are a few things before we can help you:

  • Try a more recent version of the source. Bazel is still pre 1.0, which means it has a lot of backwards incompatible changes. With your bazel version (0.16.1) it is possible the combination will just not work.
  • Share the full bazel output using pastebin, or a similar service.
